item.author: rinetd@163.com (rinetd)
item.description: server { listen 80; server_name www.your-teleport-domain.com; location / { proxy_set_header Host $host; proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr; proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:7190; # 以下三行是websocket需要的 proxy_http_version 1.1; proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade; proxy_set_header Connection "upgrade"; } }
